Package com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.method

Provides the interfaces to be implemented by native capable classes (user defined or predefined) related to methods.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CFieldMethod The CFieldMethod is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible exported C fields of DLLs from Java seen as methods.
CMethod The CMethod is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible exported C methods of DLLs from Java.
CPPConstructor The CPPConstructor is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible exported C methods of DLLs working as constructors from Java.
CPPMethod The CPPMethod is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible C++ exported instance methods of DLLs from Java.
DLLBehavior The DLLBehavior is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible to Java DLL's exported fields and methods.
DLLMethod The DLLMethod is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible exported methods of DLLs from Java.
NativeBehavior The NativeBehavior is the interface implemented by native capable classes that bridges Java and native methods and fields (as methods).
NativeBehaviorReflection The NativeBehaviorReflection is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible Java fields and methods from native seen as methods.
NativeBehaviorReflectionArray The NativeBehaviorReflectionArray is the interface implemented by native capable classes working as wrappers of one-dimensional reflection object arrays (Field[], Method[], Constructor[]).

NativeConstructor The NativeConstructor is the interface implemented by native capable classes that bridges Java and native constructors.
